data.content:
Danh từ
[lượng] đầy mắt
get an eyeful of sand
bị cát vào đầy mắt
(khẩu ngữ) cảnh đẹp đáng ngắm, cảnh ưa nhìn
she's quite an eyeful
cô ta quả là ưa nhìn
have (get) an eyeful [of something]
(khẩu ngữ)
ngắm nhìn hồi lâu (cái gì thích thú, hiếm thấy)

noun
[singular] informal
something that is very surprising, attractive, etc., to look at
The view of the mountains is an eyeful.
an attractive person :a beautiful woman
She's a real eyeful!
get/have an eyeful
If you get/have an eyeful of something or if someone gives you an eyeful of something, you see it very clearly or you see a lot of it or too much of it.
They wanted to see nature and got an eyeful during the camping trip. These phrases often refer to seeing something shocking, such as a person who is naked.
I opened the door to the locker room and got quite an eyeful.
